SIMPLE: highlight
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: highlight
<hw>highlight</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To emphasize or
call attention to, by moving into the foreground or otherwise making
more prominent.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> foreground, spotlight, play up.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To make (part of a text or image) more prominent,
especially by making it of a lighter hue or of a different color than
the remaining part.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>highlight</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: highlight
<hw>highlight</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The part of an image that has the
most intense light.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The most memorable or enjoyable part; -- of events
or activities; <as>as, the <ex>highlight</ex> of our trip was the tour
of the Vatican</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>High-low</ent>⟦br⟧
